    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "European Association of National Productivity Centres"@en, "Evropské sdružení vnitrostátních center pro produktivitu"@cs, "Associação Europeia de Centros Nacionais de Produtividade"@pt, "Europska udruga nacionalnih centara za produktivnost"@hr, "Европейска асоциация на националните центрове по производителността"@bg, "Europos nacionalinių produktyvumo centrų asociacija"@lt, "Európske združenie vnútroštátnych centier produktivity"@sk, "Europejskie Stowarzyszenie Narodowych Centrów Produktywności"@pl, "Европско удружење националних центара за продуктивност"@sr, "Ευρωπαϊκή Ένωση των Εθνικών Κέντρων Παραγωγικότητας"@el, "Associazione europea dei centri di produttività nazionali"@it, "Europese Associatie van productiviteitscentra"@nl, "Nemzeti Termelékenységi Központok Európai Szervezete"@hu, "Comhlachas Eorpach na Lárionad Náisiúnta Táirgiúlachta"@ga, "Association européenne des centres nationaux de productivité"@fr, "Euroopan tuottavuuskeskusten liitto"@fi, "Sammenslutningen af Europæiske Produktivitetscentre"@da, "Evropsko združenje nacionalnih centrov za produktivnost"@sl, "Europeiska sammanslutningen av nationella produktivitetscenter"@sv, "Europäische Vereinigung Nationaler Produktivitätszentren"@de, "Euroopa Riiklike Tootlikkuskeskuste Liit"@et, "Asociación Europea de Centros Nacionales de Productividad"@es, "Asociația Europeană a Centrelor Naționale de Productivitate"@ro, "Assoċjazzjoni Ewropea taċ-Ċentri Nazzjonali tal-Produttività"@mt, "Eiropas Nacionālo ražīguma centru apvienība"@lv;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European Association of National Productivity Centres was established as a successor body to the European Productivity Agency. Its purpose is \"to facilitate and increase exchanges of information and experiences, and arrange co-operation among participating bodies\". Membership in the Association is open to all ‘national productivity centres’ or institutions deemed their equivalent within the member states of the ‘United Nations Economic Commission for Europe’."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "EANPC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "EANPC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0001301"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "EANP"@nl, "EANP"@bg, "EANP"@hu, "EANP"@en, "EANP"@mt, "EANP"@fi, "EANP"@ga, "EANP"@es, "EANP"@sl, "EANP"@el, "EANP"@cs, "EANP"@hr, "EANP"@lt, "EANP"@de, "EANP"@pl, "EANP"@et, "EANP"@lv, "EANP"@it, "EANP"@sv, "EANP"@sk, "EANP"@da, "EANP"@pt, "EANP"@ro;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/EANPC_1966_0>;
