    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#inScheme> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#topConceptOf> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Comhairle na hÁise agus an Aigéin Chiúin"@ga, "Azijsko-pacifičko vijeće"@hr, "Consiliul Asia-Pacific"@ro, "Asian and Pacific Council"@da, "Asian and Pacific Council"@en, "Azijos ir Ramiojo vandenyno taryba"@lt, "Kunsill tal-Asja u l-Paċifiku"@mt, "Consiglio dell’Asia e del Pacifico"@it, "Asian and Pacific Council"@sv, "Ázsiai és Csendes-óceáni Tanács"@hu, "Azijsko-pacifiški svet"@sl, "Азиатски и Тихоокеански съвет"@bg, "Aasian ja Tyynenmeren maiden neuvosto"@fi, "Rada pro Asii a Tichomoří"@cs, "Asiatisch-Pazifischer Rat"@de, "Rada Azji i Pacyfiku"@pl, "Συμβούλιο Συνεργασίας Ασίας και Ειρηνικού"@el, "Consejo de Asia y el Pacífico"@es, "Āzijas un Klusā okeāna Padome"@lv, "Conselho da Ásia e do Pacífico"@pt, "Aasia ja Vaikse Ookeani Riikide Nõukogu"@et, "Raad van Azië en de Stille Oceaan"@nl, "Conseil de l’Asie et du Pacifique"@fr, "Ázijská a pacifická rada"@sk;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Asian and Pacific Council a regional organization in the Far East and in the western part of the Pacific Ocean. It was created to promote economic, cultural, scientific, and social cooperation between its member states."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "ASPAC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "ASPAC"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001050"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
