    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Agenzia per l’energia nucleare"@it, "Nuclear Energy Agency"@en, "Agentschap voor kernenergie"@nl, "Kerneenergiagenturet"@da, "Atomenergia-ügynökség"@hu, "Agence pour l’énergie nucléaire"@fr, "Tuumaenergiaagentuur"@et, "Agentura pro jadernou energii"@cs, "Agencja Energii Jądrowej"@pl, "Kernenergie-Agentur"@de, "Agência para a Energia Nuclear"@pt, "Agencija za jedrsko energijo"@sl, "Агенция за атомна енергия"@bg, "Agencia para la Energía Nuclear"@es, "An Ghníomhaireacht um Fhuinneamh Núicléach"@ga, "Aġenzija tal-Enerġija Nukleari"@mt, "Kärnenergibyrån"@sv, "Agencija za nuklearnu energiju"@hr, "Branduolinės energetikos agentūra"@lt, "Agenția pentru Energie Nucleară"@ro, "Agentúra pre jadrovú energiu"@sk, "Ydinenergiajärjestö"@fi, "Οργανισμός Πυρηνικής Ενεργείας"@el, "Kodolenerģijas aģentūra"@lv;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "NEA is an intergovernmental agency whose mission is to assist its member countries in maintaining and further developing, through international co-operation, the scientific, technological and legal bases required for a safe, environmentally friendly and economical use of nuclear energy for peaceful purposes."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "NEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001007"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>, "NEA"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>;
