    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Międzynarodowa Organizacja ds. Migracji"@pl, "Organizația Internațională pentru Migrație"@ro, "Mednarodna organizacija za migracije"@sl, "Међународна организација за миграције"@sr, "Organizzazzjoni Internazzjonali għall-Migrazzjoni"@mt, "Kansainvälinen siirtolaisuusjärjestö"@fi, "Διεθνής Οργάνωση Μετανάστευσης"@el, "Organização Internacional para as Migrações"@pt, "Medzinárodná organizácia pre migráciu"@sk, "Organizzazione internazionale per le migrazioni"@it, "Internationale Organisatie voor Migratie"@nl, "Uluslararası Göç Örgütü"@tr, "Международна организация за миграция"@bg, "International Organization for Migration"@en, "An Eagraíocht Idirnáisiúnta um Imirce"@ga, "Nemzetközi Migrációs Szervezet"@hu, "Starptautiskā Migrācijas organizācija"@lv, "Međunarodna organizacija za migracije"@hr, "Den Internationale Organisation for Migration"@da, "Organización Internacional para las Migraciones"@es, "Rahvusvaheline Migratsiooniorganisatsioon"@et, "Internationale Organisation für Migration"@de, "Tarptautinė migracijos organizacija"@lt, "Internationella organisationen för migration"@sv, "Organisation internationale pour les migrations"@fr, "Mezinárodní organizace pro migraci"@cs;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The International Organization for Migration is an inter-governmental organization in the field of migration and works closely with governmental, intergovernmental and non-governmental partners. With 157 member states, a further 10 states holding observer status and offices in over 100 countries, IOM is dedicated to promoting humane and orderly migration for the benefit of all. It does so by providing services and advice to governments and migrants."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "IOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "IOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0000999"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#altLabel> "IOM"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2002/07/owl#sameAs> <http://publications.europa.eu/resource/authority/corporate-body/IOM_1954_0>;
