    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The Latin American Parliament (Parlatino) is a consultative assembly, a regional, permanent organization composed by the countries of Latin America and the Caribbean. It is being considered to become the legislative organ of the Community of Latin American and Caribbean States."@en;
