    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Ομάδα των Δεκαπέντε"@el, "Groep van 15"@nl, "Grúpa an 15"@ga, "Grupp ta’ 15"@mt, "15 valstu grupa"@lv, "G15 csoport"@hu, "Grupul celor 15"@ro, "15 maan ryhmä"@fi, "G15-landene"@da, "Skupina 15"@cs, "Groupe des Quinze"@fr, "Group of 15"@en, "Gruppo dei 15"@it, "Г-15"@bg, "Skupina G15"@sk, "Skupina G15"@sl, "Skupina G15"@hr, "G15"@sv, "G15"@de, "Grupa 15"@pl, "15 valstybių grupė"@lt, "Grupo de los Quince"@es, "G15 riigid"@et, "Grupo dos Quinze"@pt;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "Informal forum set up to foster cooperation and provide input for other international groups. It is composed of countries from Latin America, Africa, and Asia with a common goal of enhanced growth and prosperity. The G15 focuses on cooperation among developing countries in the areas of investment, trade, and technology. Membership has since expanded to 18 countries, but the name has remained unchanged."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "G15"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "G15"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "COB0000878"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
