    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#prefLabel> "Comité européen de coordination des normes électriques dans le marché commun"@fr, "Euroopa ühisturu elektrotehniliste standardite koordineerimise kommitee"@et, "Euroopan sähkötekniikan standardointikomitea yhteismarkkinoita varten"@fi, "Kumitat Ewropew għall-Koordinazzjoni tal-Istandardizzazzjoni tal-Elettroteknika fis-Suq Komuni"@mt, "Comité Europeu de Coordenação das Normas Elétricas no Mercado Comum"@pt, "European Committee for the Coordination of Electrotechnical Standards in the Common Market"@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#definition> "The European Committee for the Coordination of Electrotechnical Standards in the Common Market (CENELCOM) aimed at providing harmonized standards in order to eliminate trade barriers. In 1973 CENEL and CENELCOM joined up to form the European Committee for Electrotechnical Standardisation (CENELEC), which counted Austria among its members."@en;
    <http://www.w3.org/2004/02/skos/core#notation> "CENELCOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#NAC>, "CENELCOM"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#LAC>, "COB0001294"^^<http://publications.europa.eu/ontology/euvoc#XML_RECORD>;
